gov.nih.nlm.meme.integrity
Interface IntegrityVector

All Known Implementing Classes:
IntegrityVector.Default
public interface IntegrityVector

Generically represents a vector of IntegrityChecks used by an application to validate content. This class includes a default implementation of the interface.

Author:
MEME Group
